{"tid":1612340,"cid":37,"subCid":0,"title":"龍門居國慶日錄「白居二」入市","createTime":"2019-10-02T08:25:57.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-02T15:30:05.000Z","uid":23734,"like":3,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"3cf3ce4cbd822644648236542cd7802540675a6e","tid":1612340,"uid":23734,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T08:25:57.000Z","msg":"市場再錄一宗國慶假日二手買賣，有「白居二」因有住屋需要，無懼社會混亂，入市屯門龍門居。<br />\n<br />\n祥益地產高級區域經理黃慶德表示，屯門居屋龍門居12座中層B室面積431方呎，業主開價435萬，減價36萬，以399萬(綠表價)成交，呎價9258元。為屋苑7月以來再錄跌穿400萬的綠表買賣。買家為為白居二，居於同區，無懼社會混亂，今日簽約入市。原業主於2011年以115.5萬(綠表價)購入，帳面獲利283.5萬，單位升值2.5倍。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://std.stheadline.com/instant/articles/detail/1103561/%E5%8D%B3%E6%99%82-%E5%9C%B0%E7%94%A2-%E9%BE%8D%E9%96%80%E5%B1%85%E5%9C%8B%E6%85%B6%E6%97%A5%E9%8C%84-%E7%99%BD%E5%B1%85%E4%BA%8C-%E5%85%A5%E5%B8%82\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstd.stheadline.com%2Finstant%2Farticles%2Fdetail%2F1103561%2F%25E5%258D%25B3%25E6%2599%2582-%25E5%259C%25B0%25E7%2594%25A2-%25E9%25BE%258D%25E9%2596%2580%25E5%25B1%2585%25E5%259C%258B%25E6%2585%25B6%25E6%2597%25A5%25E9%258C%2584-%25E7%2599%25BD%25E5%25B1%2585%25E4%25BA%258C-%25E5%2585%25A5%25E5%25B8%2582&d=zBKsoIV%2FeLhWSsP5H2J%2BmjH2jDdsOF1PL3r%2FkI4IfR4%3D&h=595aec03\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstd.stheadline.com%2Finstant%2Farticles%2Fdetail%2F1103561%2F%25E5%258D%25B3%25E6%2599%2582-%25E5%259C%25B0%25E7%2594%25A2-%25E9%25BE%258D%25E9%2596%2580%25E5%25B1%2585%25E5%259C%258B%25E6%2585%25B6%25E6%2597%25A5%25E9%258C%2584-%25E7%2599%25BD%25E5%25B1%2585%25E4%25BA%258C-%25E5%2585%25A5%25E5%25B8%2582&h=45c3198a\" target=\"_blank\">https://std.stheadline.com/instant/articles/detail/1103561/%E5%8D%B3%E6%99%82-%E5%9C%B0%E7%94%A2-%E9%BE%8D%E9%96%80%E5%B1%85%E5%9C%8B%E6%85%B6%E6%97%A5%E9%8C%84-%E7%99%BD%E5%B1%85%E4%BA%8C-%E5%85%A5%E5%B8%82</a><br />\n<br />\n琴日屯門打到九彩，雖則話未打到龍門居嗰邊，但淨係係屯門區咩交通都無曬咁滯，咁都成交到<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n香港人對於買樓真係好有熱誠<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n仲有呢個亂世都仲敢入市買樓，真勇者<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1c088755ba066e28f488ead456c4c78d15aa3b57","tid":1612340,"uid":20368,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T10:31:59.000Z","msg":"你唔買大把人買<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6e6baa3a7d27e0f899bd89bcb9a23d332d5085cc","tid":1612340,"uid":75686,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T11:17:57.000Z","msg":"樓市只會GoGoGo<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n請大家all in接貨<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n大家一齊賺<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"04c5441cea215e13eeaef9631043e2404264fba0","tid":1612340,"uid":113922,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T11:21:32.000Z","msg":"18年白居二9月30過期, 佢唔買又要再抽過, 冇得簡"},{"pid":"27eb06ad8932ea464c77ae4b8b99d9b6d9df0f67","tid":1612340,"uid":316048,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T14:17:01.000Z","msg":"Go go Go <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f36719d8d99852d3a062cd9eb7a152794945a11d","tid":1612340,"uid":23734,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"04c5441cea215e13eeaef9631043e2404264fba0","tid":1612340,"uid":113922,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T11:21:32.000Z","msg":"18年白居二9月30過期, 佢唔買又要再抽過, 冇得簡"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T15:23:44.000Z","msg":"竟然<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"61c72c2ac39732c1783c66dfe9ff7a89857d98ae","tid":1612340,"uid":235025,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T15:30:05.000Z","